  "texts": [
    "According to the authors' findings, LLMs frequently deliver false positive results when detecting smart contract vulnerabilities.",
    "This might be connected with interference from incomplete codes or LLMs' incapacity to understand code segments.An LLM can be used to build a scenario comparable to an attacker's strategy for gaining access to an organization's property by exploiting a vulnerability.",
    "Garvey et al. [29] study the viability of using Generative-AI to improve the development of Red Team scenarios in organizations.",
    "The authors [29] propose employing LLMs to construct narratives based on prompts or questions as input.",
    "Subsequently, subject-matter specialists provide remarks, including modifying narratives, adding new elements, or integrating multiple items to develop more complex scenarios."
